<exercise checkit-seed="0006" checkit-slug="IntAreaUnder" checkit-title="Area under curves">
    <statement>
        <p>
            Answer the following questions concerning
            <m>f(x)=6 \, x^{2} - 18 \, x - 24</m>.
        </p>
        <ol>
            <li>
                <p>
What is the total area between <m>f(x)=6 \, x^{2} - 18 \, x - 24</m> and the <m>x</m>-axis
from <m>x=1</m> to <m>x=8</m>?
                </p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>
What is the net area between <m>f(x)=6 \, x^{2} - 18 \, x - 24</m> and the <m>x</m>-axis
from <m>x=1</m> to <m>x=8</m>?
                </p>
            </li>
        </ol>
    </statement>
    <answer>
         <ol>
            <li>
                <p>
                    <me>
\left| \int_{ 1 }^{ 4 } 
\left( 6 \, x^{2} - 18 \, x - 24 \right) dx \right| +
\left| \int_{ 4 }^{ 8 } 
\left( 6 \, x^{2} - 18 \, x - 24 \right) dx \right| = 449
                    </me>
                </p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>
                    <me>
\int_{ 1 }^{ 8 } 
\left( 6 \, x^{2} - 18 \, x - 24 \right) dx = 287
                    </me>
                </p>
            </li>
        </ol>
    </answer>
</exercise>
